      "description": "Immediately after the caster teleports away, each creature within 10 feet of the origin space makes a Constitution save, taking 3d10 Thunder damage on a failure or half as much on a success; the boom is audible up to 300 feet away, and each slot level above 3 adds +1d10 damage.",
